Boost package prefix.

Target triple: @TARGET_TRIPLE@
Target kind: @TARGET_KIND@
Boost version: @BOOST_VERSION@

This prefix contains Boost headers and shared Boost libraries built by
develop_suit packages/boost.

Installed compiled Boost libraries:
  boost_atomic
  boost_chrono
  boost_date_time
  boost_filesystem
  boost_serialization
  boost_system
  boost_thread

Linux packages also include the LLVM C++ runtime libraries used by the shared
Boost libraries. Ordinary static archives are intentionally removed after
install; MinGW import libraries ending in .dll.a are preserved.
